Littles Baby Powder Puff (Yellow) Price: Rs.90

Keeping your baby clean and hygienic will keep them in a happy
column15:
playful and friendly mood for the entire day. Applying a fresh and pleasant powder to the baby’s body will keep them smelling good and sweat-free for the day.

The Littles Baby Powder Puff is designed especially to provide your baby with a beautiful and fun experience as you dab the powder over his body. The Extra Soft Puff provides them with the gentle caress they deserve and spreads the powder equally all over the body. The material used for the manufacture of this Powder Puff is of Non-Toxic Material so that it does not cause any undue harm to the baby’s body. The Littles Baby Powder Puff is made to be Durable for long-term use and can be conveniently used for both girls and boys.

Littles Dry Robe Bath Robe (Blue) Price: Rs.400

Babies are fond of warmth and cuddling as they are used to it in the mother’s womb. After your baby is born
column15:
as parents you will want to make sure that they stay warm and cozy all the time. To help you in doing this you can use the Dry Robe from Little\u2019s. This robe that doubles up as a quilt and a carry blanket for the baby is made of 100 per cent cotton. The cotton fabric will retain ample heat and keep the infant\u2019s body warm and keep the little one comfortable. The adorable animal prints on this Little\u2019s Dry Robe make it aesthetically appealing.

\r\n

\r\n\tYou can wrap your bundle of joy in this cozy little robe and take them out on walks. The tiny tot will remain comfortable all the while and you can be sure that the child does not contract any illnesses due to cold.
